{"id":122957,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：骚乱严重影响海地救援行动/","date":"2010-11-17T17:16:52Z","modified":"2010-11-17T17:16:52Z","title":"简讯：骚乱严重影响海地救援行动","content":"<div>\n<p>联合国说，对海地联合国救援人员的攻击严重影响了防治霍乱的工作。</p>\n<p>联合国的一份声明说，骚乱导致航班被取消、水净化工程和培训项目减少。</p>\n<p>在对一个仓库的攻击行动中，500吨食品被抢劫与焚毁。</p>\n<p>发生骚乱的原因是一些海地民众认为联合国维和部队应对传播霍乱负责。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ue9_W0S0qZDHzuK20yA7ZuKQVF0/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ue9_W0S0qZDHzuK20yA7ZuKQVF0/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ue9_W0S0qZDHzuK20yA7ZuKQVF0/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/Ue9_W0S0qZDHzuK20yA7ZuKQVF0/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=gcDKx3-cmCI:qJJiO_1iM1w:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=gcDKx3-cmCI:qJJiO_1iM1w:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=gcDKx3-cmCI:qJJiO_1iM1w:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=gcDKx3-cmCI:qJJiO_1iM1w:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=gcDKx3-cmCI:qJJiO_1iM1w:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=gcDKx3-cmCI:qJJiO_1iM1w:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/gcDKx3-cmCI\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp